Name: Ride Me

Genre: Race 

System requirements:
* Operating system: Windows (all versions)  
* Processor: 32-bit (x86)

Slogan: 
Find your balance in motion and be the best among BMX riders

Short description: 
The passage of racing tracks as bmx racers, controlling their strength and fatigue in order to go faster and jump higher.

Full description:
Sataur and Drawster riders know no barriers and are ready to conquer any trails to prove their advantage and deliver the best result.
Collect RM medals while passing obstacles and improve your skills. You must control your speed, jumps and strength to achieve the best results.
